<p style="margin:4pt 0 4pt 18pt;text-indent:-12pt;">5. [Fundamental Scoring](#5-fundamental-scoring)</p>
<p style="margin:4pt 0 4pt 18pt;text-indent:-12pt;">6. [Buy / Watch / Avoid Decision Logic](#6-buy--watch--avoid-decision-logic)</p>
